  <sentence id="s67">
   <ns/>
   <tok>
    <orth>4</orth>

 <chunk id="ch221" type="p">
  <sentence id="s221">
   <tok>
    <orth>być</orth>
    <lex disamb="1"><base>być</base><ctag>inf:imperf</ctag></lex>
   </tok>
   <tok>
    <orth>krótszy</orth>
    <lex disamb="1"><base>krótki</base><ctag>adj:sg:nom:m1:com</ctag></lex>
